data.title: Extra Virgin Olive Oil
data.text:
Item # 1010

Vigo 8.5 fl. oz Extra Virgin Olive Oil

$6.28

Single Unit - 8.5 fl. oz

Quantity

Cold-pressed Extra Virgin Olive Oil reflects the union of the earth's finest elements: fertile soil, sunny climate and the freshly-squeezed fruit of centuries-old olive trees. This earthy, robust oil captures the true essence of olives. Drizzle over hot soups or vegetables, pour over salads or simply dip crusty bread into a small bowl of salted, peppered oil to enjoy unaltered taste.
